      <title>分析师表示，中国削减汽车首付的计划可能会落空</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，中国通过削减汽车贷款首付来促进汽车销售的努力可能会因价格战和消费者谨慎而受挫，这主要有利于特斯拉和蔚来等少数受年轻买家青睐的品牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-plan-cut-downpayments-cars-likely-fall-flat-analysts-say-2024-03-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
